'''''Coast of Skeletons''''' ni filime yo kwidagadura yo mu [[Bwongereza]] na [[Afurika]] yo mu 1965, iyobowe na Robert Lynn ikinwamo na Richard Todd na Dale Robertson . Ni urukurikirane rwa filime yo mu 1963 ''y’urupfu ku Ruzi'', kandi kimwe n’iyo filime, ikoresha abantu bavugwa mu gitabo cya Edgar Wallace cyo mu 1911 cyitwa ''Sanders of the River'' na Zoltán Korda yo muri 1935 ishingiye kuri roman, ariko igashyirwa mu inkuru itandukanye rwose. ''Coast of Skeletons'' yarekuwe mubudage nka ''Sanders und das Schiff des Todes'' / ''Sanders hamwe nubwato bwurupfu'' .

Nyuma y'ubwigenge, ubukoloni bw’Abongereza butavuzwe izina aho Komiseri Harry Sanders amaze imyaka myinshi akorera yirukanywe n'abapolisi b’Ubwongereza. Sanders rero asubira i Londres, aho yahise abona akazi mu isosiyete y'ubwishingizi, ishaka ko yakurikirana umushinga wo gucukura diyama mu mazi magari yo muri Afurika y'Epfo .

